A trivial solution of the system of nonlinear differential equations of motion exists for q1 = q2 = 0. However, at the critical point or rather threshold (which denotes the onset of SPDC), this trivial solution becomes unstable in favour of a stable solution with \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
